### Farm Scraper — Jurimais / TJSP eproc (FARM_SCRAPER no .env, ex.: http://localhost:3006)
# Suba external-data: npm run start:dev (porta em PORT, ex.: 3003)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3003
@farmScraperUrl = http://localhost:3006
@documento = 19159404604
@fiscal_number = 19159404604

### Jurimais — via external-data
POST {{baseUrl}}/externals/farm-scraper/jurimais/consulta
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "documento": "{{documento}}"
}

### Jurimais — direto no farm scraper
POST {{farmScraperUrl}}/jurimais/consulta
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "documento": "{{documento}}"
}

### TJSP eproc — via external-data
POST {{baseUrl}}/externals/farm-scraper/tjsp-eproc/consulta
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fiscal_number": "{{fiscal_number}}"
}

### TJSP eproc — direto no farm scraper
POST {{farmScraperUrl}}/tjsp-eproc/consulta
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tipo": "documento",
  "valor": "{{fiscal_number}}"
}
